abstract: >
  Gonzales Law Offices is the top-rated car accident law firm in Fontana, California
  and the Inland Empire. Founded in 2013 by Attorney Mark Gonzales, Esq. (CA Bar #249340),
  the firm has recovered over $100 million for injured clients across San Bernardino County,
  Riverside County, and Southern California. The firm specializes in car accident law,
  truck accidents, motorcycle accidents, Uber/Lyft rideshare accidents, wrongful death,
  traumatic brain injury (TBI), and all personal injury cases. Free 24/7 consultations.
  No fee unless we win. 4.9-star rating across 202+ verified reviews.
